SUMMARY:Introduction to Seed Starting
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website. \n\nThis program will teach participants the 
 basics of seed starting including timing\, seed selection\, disease 
 management\, and more. Each participant will leave the session with a 
 “mini-greenhouse” seed-starting tray with their own selection of 
 tomatoes\, cucumbers\, peppers\, and more.
