X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Temple Ner Tamid": "https://nertamid.org/event/how-to-make-your-seder-more-engaging-workshop/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:nertamid
X-SOURCE:Temple Ner Tamid
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.nertamid.org/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T113000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T123000
DTSTAMP:20260321T225239
CREATED:20260226T130527Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T130527Z
UID:10003486-1774179000-1774182600@nertamid.org
SUMMARY:How to Make Your Seder More Engaging Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Join us at TNT on Sunday\, March 22nd at 11:30am for a fun\, participatory workshop with author Dr. Murray Spiegel and learn how to make your seder night truly “different from all other nights!” \nDr. Spiegel’s innovative seders have been featured in The New York Times and on PBS\, and this intriguing\, humorous\, multimedia presentation has inspired unforgettable seders around the world. \nIn this workshop you will discover music\, games\, parodies\, and quizzes\, historic and global Jewish cultural connections\, and how Shakespeare\, Donald Duck\, Klingons\, lawyers\, Phoenicians\, and Jews around the world “ask” the Four Questions.  \nCLICK HERE TO REGISTER! \n 
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/how-to-make-your-seder-more-engaging-workshop/
CATEGORIES:Adult Education
END:VEVENT
