BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Local News": "https://montclairlocal.news/event/special-screening-tokyo-story-1953/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairlocal
X-SOURCE:Montclair Local News
X-SOURCE-URL:https://montclairlocal.news/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T163000
DTSTAMP:20260321T225224
CREATED:20260219T025541Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T025541Z
UID:10138162-1774188000-1774197000@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Special Screening: TOKYO STORY (1953)
DESCRIPTION:A profoundly stirring evocation of elemental humanity and universal heartbreak\, TOKYO STORY is the crowning achievement of the unparalleled Yasujiro Ozu. The film\, which follows an aging couple’s journey to visit their grown children in bustling postwar Tokyo\, surveys the rich and complex world of family life with the director’s customary delicacy and incisive perspective on social mores. Featuring lovely performances from Ozu regulars Chishu Ryu and Setsuko Hara\, TOKYO STORY plumbs and deepens the director’s recurring theme of generational conflict\, creating what is without question one of cinema’s mightiest masterpieces.\nThis special collaboration between Montclair Film and La Cinémathèque celebrates Lives Remembered: Japanese Cinematic Masterpieces. Featuring a special introduction and Q&A with curator\, Gerard Amsellem\, local teacher\, artist\, and filmmaker from New Wave Productions along with Dr. Anne Giblin Gedacht\, Ph.D.\, Associate Professor at Seton Hall University on Japanese culture.\nPresented in Partnership with La Cinémathèque Film Club and New Wave Productions. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/special-screening-tokyo-story-1953/
LOCATION:The Clairidge\, 486 Bloomfield Ave\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community,Film
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/MV5BMTkyMjY3MTYxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0ODk5MTE@._V1_QL75_UX620_.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Film":MAILTO:info@montclairfilm.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Local News": "https://montclairlocal.news/event/spring-ritual-an-early-music-concert/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairlocal
X-SOURCE:Montclair Local News
