CREATED:20260307T211942Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260307T211942Z
UID:10138231-1774188000-1774198800@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Spring Ritual: An Early Music Concert
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to be part of something magical at New Jersey Early Music’s (NJEM) debut concert\, Spring Ritual ✨🧝 \nWith musical selections from early Medieval centuries to the richness of the Baroque era. We will be taking a journey cross traditions and cultures\, exploring ancient celebrations\, beliefs\, and ceremonies that marked the coming of spring. Featuribg period instruments\, Celtic music\, and guest artists Aléhli. A celebration of Life\, Love\, and Friendship. \nCasual reception with light refreshments to immediately follow the performance for a special Meet & Greet. Costumes and garb encouraged! Don your favorite whimsical outfit and join the magical fun! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/spring-ritual-an-early-music-concert/
LOCATION:UU Congregation at Montclair\, 67 Church Street\, Montclair\, NJ\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/inbound1032956696683468367.png
ORGANIZER;CN="New Jersey Early Music":MAILTO:Info@njearlymusic.org
END:VEVENT
