SUMMARY:The Tomeka Reid/Marty Ehrlich Duo
DESCRIPTION:A dream duo. MacArthur fellow Tomeka Reid (cello) and master 
 multi-instrumentalist Marty Ehrlich (sax/clarinets/flutes( extend the duo 
 legacy of cellist Abdul Wadud and saxophonist/flautist Julius Hemphill. 
 Featuring new compositions by Reid and Ehrlich\, and Hemphill's protean 
 works for his duo with Wadud. Do. Not. Miss. This.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Auditorium\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
