 ep end)\nImproving breath control in the water\nLearn alternate kicks (Do
 lphin Kick)\nIntroduction to and/or improving your breaststroke\nSwimming
  laps\nIntroduction to open and flip turns\nIntroduction to Butterfly\n\n
 How do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Mont
 clair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStudent Recre
