X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Local News": "https://montclairlocal.news/event/bring-your-baby-matinees-at-montclair-film-cinemas-project-hail-mary/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairlocal
X-SOURCE:Montclair Local News
X-SOURCE-URL:https://montclairlocal.news/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T120000
DTSTAMP:20260321T225224
CREATED:20260316T232715Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T232715Z
UID:10138256-1774432800-1774440000@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:BRING YOUR BABY Matinees at Montclair Film Cinemas! - PROJECT HAIL MARY
DESCRIPTION:Come see a newly released film in an environment that’s friendly to parents and caregivers of new babies. Crying babies and nursing mothers welcomed. Socialize with other new parents and bond over the joys of parenthood. No judgment. Just movies. \nJoin us next on Wednesday\, March 25 at 10:00am at The Clairidge for PROJECT HAIL MARY. \nLights will be dimmed but not off and the volume moderated. Closed Captions will be turned on.  Guests are free to move around as needed. Children under 2 are free. \nWe’re all in the same boat. Sometimes you just need to get out of the house. No babysitters required. \nThis program is Sponsored by Partnership for Maternal & Child Health of Northern New Jersey. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/bring-your-baby-matinees-at-montclair-film-cinemas-project-hail-mary/
LOCATION:The Clairidge\, 486 Bloomfield Ave\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/PHM_1-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Film":MAILTO:info@montclairfilm.org
END:VEVENT
