 ll discuss using Boolean searching tools to manipulate search results\, h
 ow to engage with database thesauri and a controlled vocabulary\, linked 
 subject headings\, setting up search alerts\, and more.\nRegister Here: h
 ttps://montclair.libcal.com/event/16500101\n\nHosted by: Sprague Library\
