DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T133000
SUMMARY:The Growth of the Semantic Layer in the Age of AI and LLMs: Unlock
 ing the Next F
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nThere is no question that the worlds of art
 ificial intelligence (AI) and large language models (LLMs) are rapidly con
 verging with enterprise analytics. As organizations race to extract maximu
 m value from their data\, the need for a robust\, scalable\, and business-
 centric data architecture becomes increasingly more critical. At the heart
  of this evolution lies a transformative concept that has been around for 
 a while now: the semantic layer.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/cloud-data-driven/events/313358619/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260214T193310Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260214T193310Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
