SUMMARY:The Corner Book Club Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a lively\, librarian-led discussion of best-selling 
 author Richard Osman's first book in the series\, "The Thursday Murder 
 Club".  In a peaceful retirement village\, four unlikely friends meet 
 weekly to discuss unsolved crimes. They have a name:  The Thursday Murder 
 Club.  When a local developer is found dead with a mysterious photograph 
 left next to the body\, the Thursday Murder Club suddenly find themselves 
 in the middle of their first live case.  Can they catch the killer before 
 it's too late?!\n
