DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nThis course aims to equip participants with the essential 
 language skills needed for traveling in French-speaking countries. Students 
 delve into practical conversations focusing on everyday scenarios 
 encountered while traveling\, from ordering in restaurants to asking 
 directions. Emphasis is on real-life communication\, cultural insights\, 
 and tips for navigating in French-speaking countries.
