 register.\n\nThe key of C is a wonderful key for beginning students. 
 Intermediate students will start to learn songs in additional keys\, will 
 learn a variety of strumming patterns\, and will learn to play melodic 
 solos on the ukulele.  Students will learn ensemble pieces: duets\, trios\, 
 and full-class numbers.  Prerequisite: Students should have completed 
 Beginning Ukulele or should be conversant with playing other fretted 
 instruments.\n
