SUMMARY:Ping Pong Party - North Jersey 
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nWe'
 re a group of people who will casually hit the ball around and rotate play
 ing to 10 or 15 points for two to three hours. If there's an interest\, we
  may do king of the hill\, round robin or set up a small tournament.\n\nAl
 l are welcome!! It's just casual fun! Come anytime! We're not in a league 
 and are not here to analyze your form.\n\nWe'll be heading indoors to the 
 table tennis tables at Ready to Golf\, 3 New Bridge Road in River Edge. We
 'll likely have pizza delivered or hang out some more at Coach House Diner
 \, 55 Rte 4 in Hackensack.\n\nReady to Golf has a lot to offer\, including
  rentable table tennis tables\, and comes as a recommendation of Joe\, one
  of our many regulars.\n\nWe'll be reserving four or five tables for singl
 es and doubles play but will get more if they're available and more than 2
 0 people show up.\n\nThe rental price covers paddles and balls. Final pric
 ing will be somewhere in the neighborhood of $10-15 per person. Please bri
 ng cash to pay for what you owe! We'll settle the bill before play.\n\nFor
  planning purposes\, we also ask that if you're stopping by later than 8 p
 .m.\, that you please let me know by commenting below\, or calling or text
 ing me.\n\nThere is a snack bar on site\, but it's only open until 7:30 p.
 m. There are some bottled drinks available and a water fountain\, but you'
 re welcome to bring food and beverages from the outside. It's BYOB friendl
 y. There's also plenty of seating and space for hanging out on the side wh
 en not playing and some televisions with sports programming.\n\nIf interes
 ted in learning more about the place\, here's the website: www.readytogolf
 .com\n\nHope you'll join us for our fifth ping pong event. Questions\, com
 ments\, concerns or having trouble finding us? You can message Andy Milone
  on Meetup\, or call/text him at 201-234-9609.\n\nIf interested\, check ou
 t one of our many other events. We do bowling\, volleyball\, tennis\, socc
 er\, hiking\, martial arts\, billiards\, dancing and bar crawls: [www.meet
 up.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball](https://www.meetup.com/nort
 h-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/313037354/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260124T172422Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260124T172422Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
