DESCRIPTION:The Department of Art & Design invites you to From the Basemen
 t\, the BFA Visual Communications Design 2026 Graduate Exhibition. Join u
 s at the Finley Gallery from March 25 to April 7 to experience a dynamic 
 showcase of work by graduating VCDS students\, featuring posters\, motion
  graphics\, packaging\, editorial\, and more. Join us for the opening rec
 eption on Friday\, March 27\, 4 to 6pm.\n \nVenture into the world of gra
 phic design at the VCDS 2026 graduate exhibition\, From the Basement. Thi
 s exhibition highlights the work of graduating Visual Communication Desig
 n students and the projects they developed throughout their time in the V
 CDS BFA program. A range of mediums will be featured\, including posters\
 , motion graphics\, packaging\, editorial\, and more! Together\, these wo
 rks reflect the unique styles and creative voices of the class.\n \nFeatu
 red Designers:\nJalen Aguirre\, Ysabella De Leon\, Brett Diese\, Domenic 
 Falivene\, Anna Fronczkowski\, Tori Gallagher\, Camila Garcia\, Robert Ga
 skill\, Britany Giraldo\, David Guerra\, Audrey Hitchens\, Natalia Kurpie
 wski\, Paolo La Rosa\, Izzy Latella\, Katie Mascuch\, Caitlin Mendoza\, E
 van Okun\, Erika Oliva\, Julia Oliveri\, Christian Pajaro\, Nicole Ricci\
 , Christopher Rizzi\, Casey Ryu\, Tom Sheridan\, Michael Shimabukuro\, Ga
 bby Trezza\, Maral Tutunjian\, and Dogan Uludogan\n \nBFA Visual Communic
 ations Design Graduate Exhibition\nOpening Reception: Friday\, March 27\,
  4–6pm\nExhibition dates: March 25–April 7\, 2026\nFinley Gallery\, Finle
 y Hall\n \nCome meet the designers and celebrate their work! Support the 
 next generation of designers as they transition from academia into the pr
 ofessional world.\n\nHosted by: Art and Design\n\nAdditional Information 
 can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12352656
