DESCRIPTION:<p>Are you interested in exploring the monthly themes through 
 writing and sharing with others? The purpose of this group is to write abo
 ut the monthly theme before the meeting and share your writing with the gr
 oup. Facilitated by Dennis Kurtti\, it will be held each month on the four
 th Saturday. This is not a writing critique group\, and all levels of writ
 ing experience are welcome. If you would like to understand more about thi
 s kind of covenant group\, you can <a href="https://www.facebook.com/watc
 h/live/?ref=watch_permalink&v=385146056918019" target="_blank">watch the w
 orship service</a> held on 8/21/22\, which featured speakers from an alre
 ady existing group. To express your interest in this group\, contact Laura
  Wilson at <a href="mailto:CovenantGroups@uumontclair.org" target="_blank
 ">CovenantGroups@uumontclair.<u></u>org</a> </p><p>Join on Zoom: <a href
