SUMMARY:A Day with Matt Giordano International Yoga Teacher
DESCRIPTION:Two workshops. One day.\nJoin us at Jaipure Yoga for an immersive afternoon with Matt Giordano\, exploring intelligent movement\, strength\, and mobility through two focused practices:\n• Hips: Align\, Refine & Release (11:00 AM–1:00 PM)\n• Arm Balances: Unlock Your Potential (2:00–4:00 PM) \nEach workshop may be taken individually or bundled for a full-day experience. \nEarly Bird pricing (through March 1):\n$57 per workshop\n$108 bundle for both \nAfter March 1:\n$65 per workshop \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/a-day-with-matt-giordano-international-yoga-teacher/
LOCATION:JaiPure Yoga\, 575 Bloomfield Ave.\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Daily-Yoga-Classes-34.png
END:VEVENT
