X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup North Jersey Bowling Soccer Volleyball": "https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball/events/312931924/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_north_jersey_bowling_soccer_volleyball
X-SOURCE:Meetup: NJ Bowling, Volleyball, Tennis & More
UID:event_312931924@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025245Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T153000
SUMMARY:Casual Volleyball - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nWe'
 re a group of people who will start by hitting the ball around for the fir
 st 20-30 minutes and then will break up into 2-4 teams for two or three ho
 urs of play.\n\nIf we have more than 20 people show up\, we'll break up in
 to three or four teams of 6 (Some may have 7\, 8 or 9. Additional players 
 just rotate into play). Games will be to 10 points. Rally scoring. Winner 
 stays on (unless a team has won four straight).\n\nWe'll be heading outdoo
 rs to the hard court in Leonia off Overpeck County Pk Driveway in the Over
 peck County Park.\n\n\\*\\*\\* After playing\, we'll be likely heading to 
 Tropical Juice Bar\, an idea of regular attendee Kate\, for a drink and sn
 ack. It's located at 60 River St. in Hackensack. Feel free to join us or s
 uggest another spot for a post-volleyball hangout. \\*\\*\\*\n\nThere's no
  fee to play volleyball and nothing else you need to do besides show up. C
 ome anytime!! All are welcome!!! We're not in a league and are not here to
  analyze your form. We're more for people who haven't played in months\, m
 aybe years\, and just want to occasionally play again and hang out.\n\nDir
 ections: You can Google "Volleyball Court in Leonia" and it should come up
 . Or type 41 Willow Tree Road\, Leonia\, NJ 07605 into your GPS\, but note
  that it's not on Willow Tree Road\, just near it. Instead\, turn onto Ove
 rpeck County Pk Driveway off Fort Lee Road (Degraw Avenue). It is past the
  tennis courts and near a basketball court and track. You can try Googling
  Leonia High School as well. That should help you find it.\n\nWe don't hav
 e the court reserved and if it happens to be taken\, we may play with thos
 e already occupying it or we will try to relocate on the fly. It's certain
 ly possible that we may have to cancel that day if we can't find a suitabl
 e spot. Please keep that in mind. And if it's looking like it'll rain or s
 now\, I'll make a call on whether to cancel around an hour ahead of time.\
 n\nPlease bring a ball and net if you have them for possible use during th
 e game. Feel free to bring a speaker for music\, or snacks and drinks for 
 consumption during play.\n\nIf you have trouble finding the court or group
 \, you can call or text Andy Milone at 201-234-9609. There is plenty of pa
 rking and an open bathroom at the park.\n\nHope you'll join us for our 17t
 h volleyball event. Questions or comments? You can message Andy on Meetup\
 , or call/text him at 201-234-9609.\n\nCheck out bowling\, soccer\, volley
 ball\, tennis or one of our other activities at: www.meetup.com/north-jers
 ey-bowling-soccer-volleyball
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/312931924/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260117T191229Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260117T191229Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
