SUMMARY:Shadow Tellers: Shadow-Puppet Story Factory (All ages welcome)
DESCRIPTION:We have been marveling at the stories that emerge between 
 shadow and light since we gathered around the first fire. Let's make 
 shadow-puppet silhouettes! Kids design characters to their hearts' 
 content\, gather around cardboard theater boxes\, and explore stories 
 together. Grownups will enjoy the privilege of helping their kids cut out 
 shadow puppets and being their very first studio audience as children fill 
 the room with the light of their imaginations. Do drop in (no registration 
 required)!\n\n \n\n \n\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Storytime Room
