X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Metrotrails Hiking": "https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/313683387/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_metrotrails
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Metrotrails Hiking
UID:event_313683387@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025243Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260329T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260329T183000
SUMMARY:Philadelphia and Columbia Railroad Finale Hike
DESCRIPTION:Metrotrails: NJ\, PA\, NY Metropolitan Area Hiking and More!\n
 Join us for this point to point hike\, the final one in our effort to hike
  the entire historic route of the Philadelphia and Columbia Railroad!\nThi
 s time\, we will hike between Lancaster and Columbia. The route features b
 ack roads and trails as well\, which include a couple of side trips.\nWe'l
 l shuttle to our start point\, and walk by the current station. We'll pick
  up the historic P&C route briefly\, maybe with a side trip on a universit
 y property\, then make our way through Brubaker Park and Noel Dorwart Park
 . These parks connect and will take us parallel to the active tracks.\nWe'
 ll take a side trip to view a splendid rail bridge on this system.\nWe'll 
 head onto some streets and then onto some more paved trails\, transitionin
 g between the two where the original P&C again diverges from the still act
 ive tracks. The original route is much different into Columbia which will 
 take us along back streets to the site of the inclined plane.\nWe then fol
 low where the canal had been to the end.\nIf needed\, contact me at 908 34
 3 8374
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/313683387/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260307T181428Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260307T181428Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
