SUMMARY:Learn English Book Club
DESCRIPTION:Come expand your English vocabulary through great books! 
 Learning another language also means using that language. This is a great 
 way to read\, discuss books and learn in a safe friendly environment. Must 
 be a second language learner (English is not your first language) who is a 
 fairly proficient speaker. If you’re not sure but interested sign up and 
 take a chance!\n\n \n\nThe group will not meet on Monday\, February 16.
