SUMMARY:Social Worker Office Hours
DESCRIPTION:Appointments: 3pm & 4pm. 45 minute appointments. \n\nMargarette 
 (they/them) and Social Work Intern can assist you with a variety of 
 services. See below for details. \n\nSome of the services Margarette 
 provides to the community:\n\n\n	Connecting you with supportive services 
 such as\, housing\, healthcare\, mental health\, legal aid\, & food 
 support.\n	Assisting you in accessing unemployment\, Social Security\, 
 Medicare\, & other government assistance programs.\n	Equipping you with 
 tools and guidance for job searches\, resume building\, and navigating 
 college & job applications.\n\n
