DESCRIPTION:March 2026 \n\n\n\nTuesday\n3/3\n4:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nRoss Dress for Less – Rockaway \n\n\nThursday\n3/5\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” Art Museum~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nTuesday \n3/10\n4:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nWalmart Ledgewood \n\n\nThursday\n3/12\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” St Patrick’s Celebration ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nSaturday\n3/14\n12:00 PM – 2:00 PM\nSt Patrick’s Day Parade – Morristown \n\n\nTuesday\n3/17\n4:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nGod Father Pizzeria- East Hanover\n\n\nThursday\n3/19\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n “Thursday’s” BINGO ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nSunday \n3/22\n3:00 PM – 4:00 PM \nSongs of Ireland with Charlie Zahm & Friends \n\n\nTuesday\n3/24\n4:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nSalvation Army – Dover \n\n\nThursday\n3/26\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” Mental Health Trivia ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nSaturday \n3/28\n10:00AM – 12:00 PM \nShopping Extravaganza with crafts – Hopatcong \n\n\nTuesday \n3/31\n4:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nTarget – Rockaway \n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \nSPACE IS LIMITED!! \nTo register or for more information\, please contact:\nYecenia Revolorio – 973-334-3496 ext. 514\nWeekdays 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM \nLight refreshments will be served.\nPrizes available for winners. \nActivity is subject to change and/or cancel.
