DESCRIPTION:Join Sigma Lambda Beta International Fraternity Inc. for an op
 en panel discussion where five brothers share their personal journeys\, b
 ackgrounds\, and experiences within Greek life. This event is designed to
  give students an authentic look into what it means to be part of SLB — b
 eyond stereotypes and surface-level perceptions.\nPanelists will speak on
  their upbringing\, what led them to explore Greek life\, why they chose 
 Sigma Lambda Beta\, and how brotherhood has shaped their identity\, leade
 rship\, and college experience. Attendees will also have the opportunity 
 to ask questions and connect with brothers afterward in an informal setti
 ng.\nWhether you’re curious about culturally based Greek life\, searching
  for community on campus\, or considering joining SLB\, this is a space t
 o learn\, listen\, and engage.\nAll are welcome.\n\nHosted by: Sigma Lamb
 da Beta International Fraternity Inc.\n\nAdditional Information can be fo
 und at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12346848
