DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Polish tradition with a twist at our Śmigus-Dyngus F
 undraiser! Inspired by the Polish holiday where friends splash water on o
 ne another to welcome spring and bring good luck\, the Polish Club is giv
 ing you the chance to dump water on one of our executive board members!\n
 For a donation\, you’ll get the opportunity to take part in this playful 
 tradition and soak an exec\, all for a great cause. Every splash helps us
  raise money for future cultural events\, community service initiatives\,
  and exciting Polish Club programming.\nCome support\, bring your friends
 \, and get ready to make a splash while celebrating Polish culture in the
  most fun way possible!\n\nHosted by: Montclair State Polish Club\n\nAddi
 tional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/enga
 ge/event/12346876
