SUMMARY:One-on-One Tech Support Sessions - with Montclair Gateway to Aging in Place
DESCRIPTION:In today’s digital age\, technology has become an integral 
 part of our daily lives. While younger generations effortlessly navigate 
 through smartphones and computers\, many senior citizens have felt left 
 behind. However\, with the advent of technology improvement classes (SS/ST 
 Classes) tailored specifically for seniors\, their lives have undergone a 
 remarkable transformation!\n\nMontclair Gateway to Aging in Place is 
 offering drop-in one-on-one tech support. Bring your device and your 
 questions.\n\nPlease register!\n\nContact support@montclairgateway.com for 
 additional questions.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Classroom\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Computers & Technology
UID:LibCal-10306-15513767
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15513767
END:VEVENT
