 ility. All levels are welcome.\n\n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is 
 not required.\nFREE for students with a valid Montclair State ID\n\nWhere
  and When?\n\nEvery Wednesday\, Jan 20 - April 24\n11am - 11:45 a.m.\nStu
 dent Recreation Center - Multipurpose Room 1\n\n\n\n\n\nInstructor - Ashl
 ey\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be found
  at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12066640
