DESCRIPTION:This session outlines the final steps in the thesis submission
  process\, including required forms\, deadlines\, and electronic submissi
 on procedures. Students will learn what to expect during final review and
  how to avoid common submission issues.Who should attend: Master’s studen
 ts nearing thesis completion or planning to graduate in an upcoming term.
