DESCRIPTION:Come on out\, load up the car with your friends\, and pull up 
 for an unforgettable movie night with SLAM in Lot 60! Kick back\, relax\,
  and enjoy a film under the stars while vibing with great people and a do
 pe atmosphere. Whether you’re here for the movie\, the laughs\, or just t
 he experience\, this is the perfect way to chill\, connect\, and make mem
