SUMMARY:Transactional Data from Cosmos: Powering Search\, Analytics & Inte
 lligent Exper
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nDiscover how to transform transactional dat
 a from Azure Cosmos DB into actionable insights and intelligent experience
 s. This session explores integrating Cosmos DB with Azure Synapse for adva
 nced analytics and Azure AI Search for discoverability\, context-aware int
 eractions\, and a user-friendly UI to search or retrieve data directly fro
 m Search. Learn how to implement Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) patt
 erns and Agentic AI to build scalable\, AI-driven solutions that ensure tr
 ansactional integrity\, searchability\, and enterprise-grade security in a
  cloud-native environment.
