DESCRIPTION:Registration Open NJ Real Estate Broker 30-Hour Office Managem
 ent Course April 9 – April 23 | 5:30 PM – 9:30 PM Burgos Realty Academ
 y offers the 30-hour Office Management Broker course as part of New Jersey
 ’s required 150-hour Broker pre-licensing curriculum. This instructor-le
 d course focuses on brokerage operations\, supervision\, compliance\, risk
  management\, and leadership responsibilities required to operate a real e
 state brokerage. The full 150-hour New Jersey Broker pre-licensing require
 ment includes: 30 Hours – Ethics & Agency 30 Hours – Office Management
  90 Hours – Basic Broker Courses are taught by a licensed broker-owner\,
  real estate instructor\, and ARELLO Certified Distance Education Instruct
 or. Instruction is designed to prepare students not only to pass the broke
 r exam\, but to manage\, lead\, and operate a compliant and effective brok
 erage.
