 te ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nThursday: 4-5PM\nStudent Recreation Center - 
 Pool \n\n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can b
 e found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11933822
