X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Foundation": "https://montclairfoundation.org/event/outdoor-adventures-arbor-day-everyday-2/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairfoundation_calendar_of_events
X-SOURCE:Montclair Foundation
X-SOURCE-URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/calendar-of-events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T120000
DTSTAMP:20260321T225229
CREATED:20251216T151545Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T204144Z
UID:10005984-1775901600-1775908800@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Outdoor Adventures - Arbor Day Everyday
DESCRIPTION:Saturday\, 10:00 AM – 12:00 PM \nApril 11th – Arbor Day Everyday \nArbor Day is a day to reflect on the importance of trees in our environment. We have an abundance of beautiful trees throughout the gardens. At April’s Outdoor Adventures\, learn more about our trees as we explore their role in our environment\, their unique leaf shapes\, and what animals use trees as their homes.  \nJoin us in the gardens as you and your family explore and learn about the outdoor world through crafts\, scavenger hunts\, activity sheets and educational displays. Each program will focus on a specific theme\, and our Van Vleck Education team will guide your family through this interactive learning experience. This program is entirely outdoors\, weather dependent. Registration is required and includes everything you need to participate in the program. Designed for children ages 4 -11 but all are welcome. \nFee: FREE for Members of Van Vleck; $15 per family  for  General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to each class \n \nSponsored by  \n  \nUpcoming Outdoor Adventures: \nMay 16th – Honeybees & Hummingbirds \nWhat do bees and hummingbirds have in common? They fly and they are pollinators! Join us to learn about your local pollinators\, how they make a positive impact on our environment\, and what we can do to help them on their mission.  \n  \nJune 6th – Insect Safari  \nYou can find many different insects buzzing\, wiggling\, and crawling around the gardens. Join us for an Insect Safari at this month’s Outdoor Adventures. Create a bug inspired craft\, take a hike looking for insects\, and learn about the important roles insects play in the garden. 
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/outdoor-adventures-arbor-day-everyday-2/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Children,Family
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2025/12/rear-garden-trees-1-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
