SUMMARY:The Secret Tea Room at Van Vleck - FULL
DESCRIPTION:Seating times: \nSaturday\, April 11 \n11:30 AM – 1:00 PM\n12:00 PM – 1:30 PM\n1:00 PM – 2:30 PM\n2:30 PM – 4:00 PM\nJoin us for an enchanting Afternoon Tea in the Living Room at Van Vleck House! \nUpon arrival\, you will be offered a menu of fine teas and infusions. Your choice of tea will be brewed to perfection. Once everyone is settled in\, the tiers will arrive with freshly baked scones\, jam\, homemade clotted cream\, scrumptious sandwiches\, and\, for the Afternoon Tea\, three scrumptious desserts. We hope you will join us! \nThis event is for adults and children ages 13+. For group bookings of more than 8 guests\, please contact richard@secrettearoom.us. Seatings are 90 minutes\, and registration is required. \nDietary Restrictions\nA gluten-free option is available with prior notice. We are not able to accommodate a dairy-free or vegan diet. All requests must be communicated to us 48 hours before the event. You may note this request on the checkout page. For dietary/allergy inquiries\, please contact richard@secrettearoom.us. \nCancellation Policy\nWe are unable to accommodate cancellations or rescheduling. If you find you are no longer able to attend your scheduled event\, you may transfer your ticket(s) to another person(s) to attend instead. Please notify Van Vleck House and Gardens so we can update your ticket name(s) for event check-in. \nPlease note that this event is a fundraiser\, and a portion of your ticket price will go towards supporting our
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/the-secret-tea-room-at-van-vleck-5/
CATEGORIES:Events,Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/02/20250606_130515-scaled-e1770853846850.jpg
END:VEVENT
