DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nTri Sigma initiation is a meaningful ceremony 
 that marks the transition from new member to fully initiated sister withi
 n the sorority. It is a formal and reflective experience centered on the 
 organization’s values of wisdom\, power\, faith\, hope\, and love. During
  initiation\, members learn more deeply about Tri Sigma’s traditions\, hi
 story\, and lifelong commitment to sisterhood\, service\, and personal gr
 owth. The ceremony symbolizes belonging\, responsibility\, and the shared
  bond that connects all Tri Sigma members across chapters and generations
 .\n\n\n\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n \n\nHosted by: Sigma Sigma Sigma\n\nAdditio
 nal Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/
 event/12263360
