DESCRIPTION:Brief Description: \nNever swam before? No problem! These less
 ons will give you the important foundational skills in swimming and help 
 you be more comfortable in the pool. Learn how to use proper breath contr
 ol\, float\, and swim with a kickboard. \nSkills Focus:\n\nBeing comforta
 ble in the water\nLearning how to float on your back and front\nLearning 
 how to kick off the wall with a kickboard\nIntroducing proper breath cont
 rol in the water\nLearning how to tread water\nLearn alternate kicks (Fro
 ggy Kick)\nBeing comfortable in the deep end \nIntroducing arms to your s
 trokes\n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a 
 valid Montclair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStu
 dent Recreation Center - Pool \n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAddit
 ional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engag
 e/event/11931657
