DESCRIPTION:\nTake your swimming to the next level! Get introduced to new 
 strokes or work on the ones you already know. These lessons are for swimm
 ers who are a little more comfortable in the water but still want to impr
 ove their technique and expand what skills they know. \n \nSkills Focus:\
 n\nSwimming unassisted on your front and back \nImprove treading (in the 
 deep end)\nImproving breath control in the water\nLearn alternate kicks (
 Dolphin Kick)\nIntroduction to and/or improving your breaststroke\nSwimmi
 ng laps\nIntroduction to open and flip turns\nIntroduction to Butterfly\n
 \nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Mo
 ntclair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStudent Rec
 reation Center - Pool \n\n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional 
