DESCRIPTION:All are welcome to join the annual interfaith Yom Hashoah Holo
 caust commemoration\, hosted by the Montclair Interfaith Clergy Associatio
 n.  \n  \nAs part of the service\, we will hear from Pamela Romanchuk\, gr
 anddaughter of four Holocaust survivors\, who will share her family's stor
 ies of survival\, family\, legacy\, and the enduring strength of the Jewis
 h people.  \n  \n**Questions?**  \nContact Bnai Keshet  \n(973) 746-4889\n
 \n
