DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWOCA General Body Meetings are welcoming\, hig
 h-energy spaces where women of color come together to connect\, learn\, a
 nd grow. These meetings feature engaging discussions\, guest speakers\, a
 nd community-building activities designed to inspire leadership\, strengt
 hen sisterhood\, and provide resources for personal and professional succ
 ess. Each meeting is a chance to be seen\, heard\, and supported while bu
 ilding lasting connections. \n\n\n\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n \n\nHosted by: T
