DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Native African Student Organization's General 
 Body Meeting! This is a space where we come together to celebrate and exp
 lore the richness of African cultures\, while also connecting with other 
 cultures from around the world. At each meeting\, we'll engage in lively 
 discussions\, learn about Africa’s diverse history\, traditions\, and cur
 rent events\, and empower each other to understand and embrace our herita
 ge. Whether you're looking to deepen your cultural knowledge\, make meani
 ngful connections\, or simply have fun with fellow students who share a p
 assion for Africa and global cultures\, this is the place to be! Let’s bu
 ild a supportive community\, amplify African voices on campus\, and creat
 e lasting friendships. All are welcome\, come\, learn\, share\, and conne
 ct!\n\nHosted by: Native African Student Organization\n\nAdditional Infor
 mation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/121
 67564
