CREATED:20251216T145812Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T200137Z
UID:10005981-1776700800-1776704400@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Garden to Table - Butterfly Waffles
DESCRIPTION:Garden to Table \nMondays\, 4:00 PM – 5:00 PM \nApril 20 – Butterfly Waffles \nWhen exploring the gardens you are sure to spot monarch butterflies. Join us for our April Garden to Table class to make Butterfly Waffles\, and learn more about why monarchs are so important to have in our gardens. \nEnjoy quality time in the garden with your child/children as we explore the Edible Garden and all that it has to offer. Help us weed and water\, plant\, and harvest. We will prepare a simple snack with ingredients inspired by the garden. Appropriate for children ages 4 and up but all are welcome. Children must be accompanied by an adult. \nSponsored by  \nFee: $15/class per child for Members / $20/class per child for General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to each class
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/garden-to-table-butterfly-waffles-2/
CATEGORIES:Classes,Children
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2025/07/unnamed-4.png
END:VEVENT
