 ion\,  and living your faith by taking action for the planet. Email <a h
 ref="mailto:greenteam@fccmtc.com" target="_blank">greenteam@fccmtc.com</a>
  <b>for Zoom link.</b><br><span> </span><br><span> </span><br><span>Gre
 en Team/Creation Justice Ministry monthly meetings: 2nd Sunday of the mont
 h\, after worship\, in the FCC library. </span><span> </span><span><span>
 <span>Our congregation is committed to the idea that creation care is cen
 tral to each aspect of our church: our theology and worship\, institutiona
 l life and practices\, and our partnership and work in the wider community
 . </span></span></span><span>Learn about FCC’s climate justice initiati
 ves\, be part of planning our events\, and live your faith by taking actio
 n for the planet. </span><br><span>Check out our Green Team Ministry page
  here: </span><a href="https://fccmontclair.org/green-team-ministry/" tar
 get="_blank">https://fccmontclair.org/green-team-ministry/</a><span> <br><
 /span><span>and read our Creation Justice Covenant here: <a href="https:/
 /www.fccmontclair.org/creation-justice-church/" target="_blank">https://ww
 w.fccmontclair.org/creation-justice-church/</a></span>
