CREATED:20110321T135654Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><span>Please join us in our beautiful sanctuary for worship
  each Sunday. We will have coffee hour in the Guild Room following worship
 . <br></span></p><p><span>We will also </span><a href="https://www.faceboo
 k.com/FCCMontclair" target="_blank"><span>live stream</span></a><span> wor
 ship. You can find <a href="https://fccmontclair.org/about-us-3/this-weeks
 -bulletin/">this week's online bulletin</a> here.</span> <br></p><p><span
 ><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanently close
 d. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway is next
  to the playground. </b></span></p><u></u><u></u><u></u>
