SUMMARY:Meeting at the Verona inn!
DESCRIPTION:Board Game Night At Verona Inn\nWe will be doing our first mon
 thly meeting starting on **February 25th at the Verona Inn!** We will be m
 eeting up to organize games starting at 7:30\, with food and drinks availa
 ble courtesy of our host! You can play any game provided by hosts or bring
  your own! If you do not have a friend group to play games\, hosts will or
 ganize you into pods with other people who need players. There are **no du
 es**. Future meetings will be held on the **last Wednesday of each month.*
 *\n\nMore information and ground rules:\n\n* **The doors open at 6:30 but 
 games do not start until 7:30.** I *highly recommend* coming in during thi
 s period to eat your food and drink ahead of time!\n* **Please return the 
 graciousness provided by our hosts and order at least one item! All venue 
 specific rules apply to our club.** Future meetings depend on treating our
  hosts with respect.\n* **All games must be returned to their owners when 
 they announce that they are leaving.** If you are in a game in progress wh
 en the meeting ends but it is not borrowed you may continue playing!\n* **
 Please place food and drink on a separate table or surface from your games
 ** to help avoid stains and other damage.\n* **Please engage with others i
 n good faith\, sportsmanship\, respect and common sense.** *ABSOLUTELY NO 
 harassment\, getting physical\, hurtful insulting\, and persecutory langua
 ge will be tolerated.* Repeat violators of venue rules AND/OR this rule ma
 y be asked to leave the event and not return.
