X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: WordPress Montclair": "https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311737726/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_wordpress_montclair_meetup
X-SOURCE:Meetup: WordPress Montclair
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/
UID:event_311737726@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025251Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260723T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260723T200000
SUMMARY:Help Desk - Bring Your Laptop\, Yourself\, and Your WordPress Prob
 lems
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Montclair Meetup\nIf you are running a WordPress sit
 e and are having issues and would like some help\, then this Meetup is for
  you!\n\nIf you know some things\, expert or not\, and want to give back t
 o the WordPress community\, then this Meetup is for you too!\n\nWe will do
  our best to match a problem with a problem-solver. On-site and in real-ti
 me. Just bring yourself\, your laptop\, and your WordPress problems.\n\nIt
 's OK if you attend and only want to observe. We recognize this is how peo
 ple learn. Given our time limit of two hours\, we may not be able to solve
  everyone's issues\, but we will try! If you are seeking help\, please com
 e prepared. Have your web site loaded in a browser\, have your WordPress a
 dmin ready\, along with a short list of issues you are trying to solve.\n\
 nPeople helping are volunteers and may not be experts. There is risk to br
 eaking your site! Please do not bring client or business sites that can im
 pact reputations or revenue. If you have a staging site we can test things
  with\, that is always preferred. If it is a production site\, please crea
 te a site backup before having someone do any work on your site.\n\nIf you
  cannot find the group\, please ask the front desk where the WordPress mee
 tup group is meeting.\n\n**PARKING**:\nWe've been asked to not park in the
  United Way lot behind the library as it could result in a parking ticket.
  Please find street parking or a parking deck.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\nJoin the **Je
 rseyPress Slack** group to chat with others in our community and get help:
  [https://jerseypress.org/slack/](https://jerseypress.org/slack/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311
 737726/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251027T204810Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251027T204810Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
